  "title": "可以预见的错误",
  "image_width": 3264,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ll_koKHG\">第一本书的开场是认知偏差的一个系列：《可以预见的错误》。书中的其余部分并没有在这个话题上止步；坏习惯和坏主意事关重大，即便它们萌芽的地方是我们的思维内容，而非思维结构。</p><p data-pid=\"v1DIYVMF\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Biases-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《偏差：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"偏见（偏差）[5]：导读\" data-url=\"https://hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup> by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_1/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">我所谓的理性到底是什么意思？ - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_2/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">感受理性 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_3/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">为何寻求真实 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_4/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">何谓偏见 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_5/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">可获得性 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_6/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">繁琐的细节 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_7/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" t